          },
          "reviewBody": "very hypocrital school! Even the students misbehaved\nthey were smoking in the bathroom\nthe washroom were terrible\nmy ward have refused to go to school after such a terrible experience\nthe school feel like it has not been renovated since 1669.\nyou first figure out that is it an international school or global school . 📉📉📉📉💔💔💔💔",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Amity International School - Section 44"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Priya Bhandari"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-04-06",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My experience with amity for admission process had been worse from the time we entered the premise, during interactions and receiving communication from them.\n\nThe staff and principal there is full of attitude and don’t treat the parents well. It started from our experience interacting at the reception itself. There  is very poor management   after multiple follow ups we received an invite for virtual interaction where they interview the child and parents. The interaction with child only focused on what they are looking for and not what child is good at or her interest. They give us hope for one month we will give admission don't worry. I was waiting till 6 April.  At last they said not clear. If u r not giving admission to child. You should say no to parents on time. At least time toh na khrab hota. Or kisi school me toh try krte. Amity me ho jayga admission krke teen school k call Missed kr diya. Kyuki amity ne bola tha ki ho jayga agr inko mna krna tha within two days me mna kr dete.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
