            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Don't ruin your ward future. It just fame of name. Govt school is more better than this. Teacher is always on bad mood.\nthey have washrooms which seem like govt. toilets and students have scribbled awful things on the doors of the washroom like who are their crush, boyfriend’s etc……and cheating is like a game for them… Students hide chits in the washrooms etc. There are literally rats and lizards in the classroom and talk about the chairs and desks….they are broken sometimes even thorns in the wood of the chair which can hurt you very badly…..now, if this is the situation of the classrooms and washrooms",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
